  <p style="font-size: 16pt">Joe stated on the Endgrain Facebook that, "This new space will not only allow us to have a much larger cafe but we will also move the roasting operation into the new space as well." With more cafe space and more space to allow for roasting, Endgrain will be taking fresh roasted coffee to the next level by having roasting just feet away from space where Endgrain's incredible team of baristas will be preparing each customer's coffee drinks.</p>
  <p style="font-size: 16pt">Of course, Joe hasn't been at it alone. He took the time to thank his family, his awesome staff, and Endgrain's hugely loyal customers for believing and for coming back time and again.</p>
